---
import hero from "../../images/hero.jpg"
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro"
---

<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center py-16 lg:py-0">
    {/* Texto del Héroe */}
    <div class="text-center lg:text-left lg:py-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl leading-tight mb-6">
        Tu salud dental es mi priodidad
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Una descripción concisa y atractiva que explica los beneficios clave y el valor que ofreces. Atrae a tu audiencia y haz que quieran saber más.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
        <a href="/agenda-tu-cita" class="px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium text-center text-white bg-primary rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-hover focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-secondary">Agenda tu cita</a>
        <a href="#servicios" class="text-primary hover:text-white border border-primary hover:bg-primary-hover focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-secondary font-medium rounded-lg text-base px-5 py-3 text-center me-2">Servicios</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-500 h-full">
      <Image src={hero} alt="" class="size-full object-cover" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>